<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/32401ANQMVQVNTGTQHTSGSGJCPVKHDGKP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Aca-May-zing Voices";
  schema:description """
	Experience the pure power of the human voice at this vibrant, all a cappella celebration. The evening brings together an exciting mix of choruses, quartets, and vocal ensembles, each offering their own signature sound—from lush harmonies and rhythmic precision to playful musical storytelling. With no instruments in sight, every beat, chord, and texture is created live, crafted through breath, blend, and bold creativity. Audiences will be treated to a dynamic journey across genres and styles as groups of all sizes take the stage, each revealing what’s possible when voices unite. Whether you’re a longtime a cappella fan or discovering the magic for the first time, this show promises warmth, artistry, and unforgettable musical moments. It’s a celebration of community, craft, and the joy of singing together.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Tickets are $30 for adults, $20 for students, and free for children 12 and under (Including taxes and fees). Seating is not assigned.  No refunds.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-06T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
