<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/18601AGJVHRJDDNTMMMDTKPLTNBGVTLHV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Chen, Cheng & Beethoven";
  schema:description """
	One of Canada’s most beloved pianists, Angela Cheng, takes center stage in Beethoven’s Piano Concerto No. 1—a sparkling, crowd-pleasing masterpiece that blends classical charm with virtuosic brilliance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From romantic comfort to modern textures, under the direction of guest conductor Monica Chen, this concert promises a rich and dynamic listening experience—familiar, fresh, and deeply engaging.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To purchase tickets, please visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://reginasymphony.com/chen-cheng-beethoven-dh/\">the RSO website.</a>
""";
