  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Dr. David Dick</span> and <span class=\"BoldText\">Mike Angell</span> perform works for trombone and piano, and solo piano, by Henri Busser, Castarede, Nassara, and Raum.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Admission is free.</span>
