<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/10601APSKMRRDLKDGKBKNPNLTDRGCSHLR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Delhi 2 Dublin";
  schema:description """
	For nearly two decades, <span class=\"BoldText\">Delhi 2 Dublin</span> has been at the forefront of South Asian fusion music, pioneering a global bass sound they call \"Subcontinental Pop\"- a high-energy blend of Bhangra, electronic, hip-hop, reggae, and Celtic influences that defies genre and unites dancefloors worldwide. As they approach their 20th anniversary in 2026, members Sanjay Seran, Ravi Binning, Serena Eades and new addition Kal Mattu continue to push the band’s sound and vision to new heights, leading them into an exciting new chapter of music-making after a six-year hiatus. What started as a one-night collaboration at Vancouver’s Celtic Fest in 2006 has evolved into a world-touring phenomenon, gracing legendary stages like Electric Forest, Glastonbury, Burning Man, Bali Spirit Festival, and Woodford Folk Festival while captivating audiences from Mumbai to Nevada. Known for their high-energy, genre-defying performances, Delhi 2 Dublin delivers what fans describe as \"90 minutes of freebasing joy.\"<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Premium seating is $50, Standard seating is $40, and Economy seating is $30. Prices are inclusive of taxes and fees. Seating is assigned.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-01T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
