<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/34201ASMCSDCJKPKGCLJTKVRDGQJPPMJH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Regina Music Festival Final Competition";
  schema:description """
	The <span class=\"BoldText\">Regina Music Festival</span> invites the community to attend two outstanding showcase events featuring some of this year’s top performers. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>At <span class=\"BoldText\">1 pm</span>, the <span class=\"BoldText\">MLT Aikins Junior Competition</span> will feature two performers from the junior classes in each of the disciplines of Piano, Strings, Brass & Winds, Voice, and Musical Theatre as they compete for the final grand prize. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>At <span class=\"BoldText\">7 pm</span>, the <span class=\"BoldText\">Regina Central Lions Club Senior Competition</span> will showcase two additional outstanding performers selected from the senior classes. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>These special events celebrate the dedication, artistry, and achievement of young musicians in our community. Join us in recognizing and supporting this exceptional local talent.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Admission is free.</span>
""";
