<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/32801AVMKCMLRNPSSSQQTHRKHHMLJSPPT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Seven:  Living and Learning at Ranch Ehrlo ";
  schema:description """
	An original musical inspired by the Seven Grandfather Teachings – celebrating courage, culture, and community.  Performed by participants in Ranch Ehrlo’s Supported Living program and Youth Group Living Treatment Program, led by certified music therapists.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come experience the power of music – and the courage of these incredible performers.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Silver collection accepted at the door through the NMC Music Therapy Initiative, and with thanks to the generosity of the Jim Pattison Foundation, every dollar donated will be matched – doubling your impact and helping more Canadians experience the healing power of music.
""";
