  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Teagan Littlechief";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Teagan Littlechief</span> is a dynamic country rock artist with a voice that captivates and a spirit that inspires. Known for her powerhouse vocals and commanding stage presence, Teagan is one of Canada’s leading Indigenous musicians. She is the 2025 SaskMusic Contemporary Indigenous Artist of the Year, the 2024 SCMA Female Artist of the Year, and is a three-time SCMA Indigenous Artist of the Year recipient.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Premium seating is $50, Standard seating is $40, and Economy seating is $30. Prices are inclusive of taxes and fees. Seating is assigned.</span>
