<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/28801AVBKQSCSGSCMSTRKBBJTVJRJMRQJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "TEDxRegina 2026:  Once Upon Our Future";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">TEDxRegina 2026</span> is a full-day experience designed to inspire, challenge, and bring our community together.  This year’s experience brings together storytellers, innovators, community leaders, and visionaries who are shaping the world we want to see.  Through two inspiring sessions, attendees will explore how our shared stories, values, and actions can build a future that is more compassionate, creative, and connected.  Join us as we reimagine what’s possible and write the next chapter of our shared future, one idea at a time.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For more information and to purchase tickets, visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/tedxregina-2026-once-upon-our-future-tickets-1975641689476?aff=oddtdtcreator\">Eventbrite.</a>
""";
